#strong[What choice is the current economy forcing on your characters?]


#hint[A war economy, famine, or recession doesn't just set the backdrop. It creates urgency. If the world is collapsing, falling in love might feel irresponsible, or it might be the only thing worth holding onto.]


#writing-box(
